2026-07-19 01:36:01,541 INFO Reasoning repetition stage=proof_generation detail=candidate=12 round=0 mode=opd_xml prompt_family=opd gzip_factor=3.9121 repeated_32word_windows=0.0002 (6/35752) warning=False
